text: Dono madagoaa dela gu hoohoo gi dono made, gei mee ga gahi mai dana dama daane go Joseph, ga helekai gi mee, “Dugua doo lima gi mehanga ogu gadawae.47.29 Dugua doo lima gi mehanga ogu gadawae Di hai deenei e haga modongoohia bolo di hagamodudahi dela gaa hai la di mee e deemee di huli  Heia dau hagababa hagamodu bolo goe hagalee danu au i Egypt.
